136
00:07:52,032 --> 00:07:53,956
Don't you recognize me?

137
00:07:55,156 --> 00:07:57,956
I'm His Majesty's consorts.

138
00:07:57,956 --> 00:08:01,088
Our relationship is above reproach.

139
00:08:01,728 --> 00:08:04,196
Seems you've embraced this new identity.

140
00:08:04,196 --> 00:08:06,816
(Did the original owner
have a relationship with him?)

141
00:08:06,816 --> 00:08:08,512
(If I deny it now,)

142
00:08:08,544 --> 00:08:10,176
(would it undermine my character?)

143
00:08:10,656 --> 00:08:12,512
(Before I get the full picture,)

144
00:08:12,512 --> 00:08:14,208
(I shall placate him.)

145
00:08:14,836 --> 00:08:15,916
Your Highness,

146
00:08:15,916 --> 00:08:18,720
