154
00:08:34,836 --> 00:08:36,436
I'm quite curious about something.

155
00:08:36,436 --> 00:08:37,248
What?

156
00:08:37,408 --> 00:08:39,556
Ordinary women fear bodies.

157
00:08:39,808 --> 00:08:41,716
Why do you show no fear,

158
00:08:41,716 --> 00:08:43,596
but checked her body?

159
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,816
I happen to know medicine.

160
00:08:46,916 --> 00:08:49,632
You must be remarkable at it.

161
00:08:49,632 --> 00:08:51,264
You even know by injecting mercury,

162
00:08:51,264 --> 00:08:53,568
you can get a complete human skin.

163
00:08:55,796 --> 00:08:57,916
I happened to pass
by the palace last night.

164
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,716
Did you

165
00:08:59,716 --> 00:09:01,836
